נשׁים    - אשּׁה / 'ishshâh  - nâshîym / ish-shaw', naw-sheem'
=== Etymology ===

The first form is the feminine of [[אישׁ]] {{HH|376}} or [[אנושׁ]] {{HH|582}}; 
the second form is an irregular plural; 
=== Noun ===
a woman (used in the same wide sense as [[אנושׁ]] {{HH|582}}).: - [adulter]ess, each, every, female, X many, + none, one, + together, wife, woman. Often unexpressed in English.